snippet.title: Best VGM 2151 - Xenoblade Chronicles 2 - Land of Morytha
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Switch
Xenoblade Chronicles 2 (2017)
Land of Morytha
Yasunori Mitsuda, ACE, Kenji Hiramatsu & Manami Kiyota
